#. module: pos_avatax
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_avatax/static/src/app/services/pos_store.js:0
msgid ""
"Enable to load Avatax taxes, please verify partner information and Avatax "
"API configuration."
msgstr ""
"Tillåt att hämta skatteinformation från Avatax, vänligen kontrollera "
"partnerns kontaktinformation samt API-inställningar för Avatax."

#. module: pos_avatax
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_avatax/static/src/app/services/pos_store.js:0
